	<h1 class="title">恶搞经典电影，《辛普森一家》很有一套</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/4369/small/4369.jpg?1419239008" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">晏文静</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-01-09 08:33:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/5068/medium/5068.jpg?1436675617" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


